    // 5. Q&A Deep Dive
    const qaNote = hasQA ? '' : '\n\nNote: Q&A section was not clearly detected in this transcript — some questions below may not apply.';
    prompts.push(`Analyze the Q&A section of this ${company} ${quarter} earnings call in depth.${qaNote}

For each analyst question:

1. **Summarize the question** in one sentence
2. **Rate the answer quality** (Direct / Partially Answered / Deflected)
